lead_paragraph: Harrison Barnes made a 10-foot running jumper with 3.7 seconds left for the last of his team-high 24 points to give the Dallas Mavericks a 90-88 victory over the Los Angeles Clippers on Friday night.

headline.print_headline: Mavs Beat Clippers 90-88 on Barnes' Jumper
